Pembroke_Pines.WLTV-DT: WLTV-DT, virtual and UHF digital channel 23, is a Univision owned-and-operated television station licensed to Miami, Florida, United States and also serving Fort Lauderdale. It is one of two East Coast flagship stations of the Spanish-language network (the other being WXTV-DT in the New York City market). WLTV is owned by the Univision Local Media subsidiary of Univision Communications as part of a duopoly with Hollywood-licensed UniMás flagship WAMI-DT (channel 69).
